snippet.title: Lost Eidolons - Official Gameplay Trailer | ID@Xbox
snippet.description:
Set in an empire that is facing a civil war, the turn-based tactical RPG Lost Eidolons casts you as Eden, a charming mercenary captain who must rise above all the horrors of the land to unite the kingdoms.

#IGN #Games
